# Web UI Layout

- Prefer full-width page and dashboard layouts that use the available viewport.
- Do not add centered container wrappers such as `mx-auto max-w-*` for primary
  app chrome, page bodies, cards, tables, or descriptive copy.
- Use narrow widths only for controls that need an intrinsic size to work well,
  such as small buttons, badges, icons, or compact form fields.
